		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Bonus ending -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">At the media selection screen press R1, R2, X, L2, Square, X, Square, R2, R2, R2, X, L2, Square, X, R2, Square, L2, R2, X, L2, Square, X, R2, Square, L2, R2, X, Square</font>&nbsp;
 			<br>&nbsp; Debug mode  -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Pause the game and highlight Exit, then hold L2 and press Left, Circle, Up, Down, Right, Right, Left, Triangle, Up, Down</font>&nbsp;
 			<br>&nbsp; Infinite Lives -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Pause the game and highlight Exit, then hold L2 and press Up, Up, Down, Right, Triangle, Down</font>&nbsp;
 			<br>&nbsp; Invencibility -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Pause the game and highlight Exit, then hold L2 and press Left, Right, Triangle, Down, Right, Left</font>&nbsp;
 			<br>&nbsp; Unlock more remotes -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">While paused press Square, Circle, R1, Triangle, L1, R1, L1, R1, Circle, Circle, R1, Triangle, L1, R1, Circle, L1, Triangle, Circle, triangle, L1, R1, Circle, L1, Triangle, Circle, R1, L1</font>&nbsp;<br><br>
	 </tr>
